Package com.syncano.android.lib.modules.data

Class Summary
ParamsDataAddParent Adds additional parent to data with data_id.
ParamsDataCopy Copies data with data_id.
ParamsDataCount Counts data of specified criteria. collection_id/collection_key parameter means that one can use either one of them - collection_id or collection_key.
ParamsDataDelete Deletes Data Object.
ParamsDataGet Get data from collection(s) or whole project with optional additional filtering.
ParamsDataGetOne Get data by data_id or data_key.
ParamsDataMove Moves data to folder and/or state.
ParamsDataNew Creates a new Data Object. collection_id/collection_key parameter means that one can use either one of them - collection_id or collection_key.
ParamsDataRemoveParent Removes a parent from data with data_id. collection_id/collection_key parameter means that one can use either one of them - collection_id or collection_key.
ParamsDataUpdate Updates existing Data Object if data with specified data_id or data_key already exists.
ResponseDataCopy Response with copied data
ResponseDataCount Response with data count
ResponseDataGet Response with data array
ResponseDataGetOne Response for data get one
ResponseDataNew Response for creating new data
ResponseDataUpdate Response with updated data
